Dignity Impact as a Primary Outcome Measure for Dignity Therapy.

Scarton L(1), Oh S(1), Sylvera A(1), Lamonge R(1), Yao Y(1), Chochinov H(2)(3), 
Fitchett G(4), Handzo G(5), Emanuel L(6), Wilkie D(1).

Author information:
(1)1 University of Florida College of Nursing, Gainesville, FL, USA.
(2)2 Department of Psychiatry, University of Manitoba, Winnipeg, Manitoba, 
